articles.title: Anti-Israeli Mob Storms Airport in Russia's Dagestan - The Moscow Times
articles.description: A mob of anti-Israeli protesters stormed an airport in the North Caucasus republic of Dagestan on Sunday night following calls on social media to block a flight from Tel Aviv from landing in the majority-Muslim region.
